					<description><![CDATA[大家有没感觉，入夏前总觉火气大、人又虚，尤其阴虚者，脾胃寒湿者，舌苔白腻者更能感受到浮火！ 这时候，我推荐用「 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">大家有没感觉，入夏前总觉火气大、人又虚，尤其阴虚者，脾胃寒湿者，舌苔白腻者更能感受到浮火！</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">这时候，我推荐用</span><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">「初夏第一果」：枇杷</span></span></strong><span style="color: green;">来解春天的火和热~</span></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/b88e2dfe655936506d4871942951ddc3.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">枇杷：止渴下气、润五脏</span></span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">枇杷虽然属于春果，却</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">独备四时之气</span></span><span style="color: green;">：</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">会下火却不误伤肝脾，几颗下肚可</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">抚平上焦的火气</span></span><span style="color: green;">，同时</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">止渴下气、滋润五脏</span></span><span style="color: green;">。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">但是这些好处，仅熟透的枇杷果实才有哦。吃酸涩、未熟透的枇杷，会辅助肝木克脾土，让你越吃越脾虚。</span></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/5285354ed8fa2e8d40c29f52d2ed6a34.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">看到这，是不是想吃上几颗甜果实润喉？若嫌单吃枇杷果太单调，推荐试试</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">除烦润肺甜汤</span></span><span style="color: green;">。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">枇杷双白汤：生津养肺、清心除烦</span></span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">枇杷果清甜多汁，肉质细腻，含有保护视力、滋润肌肤的营养物质。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">将枇杷和银耳、百合同煮，可</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">滋阴补气、生津养肺、清心除烦</span></span><span style="color: green;">，尤宜这段时间饮用。</span></span></p><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">01、</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">枇杷双白汤</span></span></span>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">枇杷200g、百合8g、银耳80g、冰糖适量</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">①银耳提前泡开，再撕小朵；百合洗净后，和银耳一同入锅；</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">②大火烧开后转小火30分钟，再下剥除了果皮和果核的枇杷以及冰糖；</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">③十分钟后熄火，放凉享用。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">&#8230;</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">由于枇杷含糖量高，</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">糖尿病患者不宜食用</span></span><span style="color: green;">；</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">脾虚腹泻者亦不宜食用</span></span><span style="color: green;">，健康人群</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">过食会助生痰湿</span></span><span style="color: green;">，要注意！</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">===</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">枇杷叶：药用最广、止咳明显</span></span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">不少朋友以为，止咳枇杷膏是枇杷果肉加冰糖熬制。其实不然，枇杷膏的止咳功效得益于枇杷叶。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">枇杷叶是一味止咳中药，药用甚广，常用于</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">肺热痰嗽，阴虚劳嗽、胃热呕哕、妊娠恶阻、消渴等症状</span></span><span style="color: green;">。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">不过，用枇杷叶煎汤或熬膏或入散时，需要</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">除净表面绒毛</span></span><span style="color: green;">（避免发生呕吐、咳嗽、过敏等不良反应），</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">同时用卤料袋包好</span></span><span style="color: green;">。</span></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/cd4a46ba3f3c5db053d39ec0b58e409a.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">02、</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">枇杷双白汤</span></span></span>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">枇杷叶8g、枇杷果1000g，黄冰糖1000g，柠檬一个</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">①将枇杷叶用卤料袋装好，再将去皮去核后的枇杷果搅成泥状；</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">②柠檬切片，把所有汁液滴进果泥，再撒冰糖腌30分钟；</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">③最后慢火熬膏，再装密封瓶冷藏保存。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">&#8230;</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">想自制枇杷膏的朋友，可以尝试。食用要就温水冲服</span>。<span style="color: green;">膏方可止咳保健，但不可过度依赖。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">值得注意的是，糖尿病患者、脾胃虚弱者、妊娠和哺乳期的妇女不可食用</span></span><span style="color: green;">！</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">===</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">枇杷花：润喉润肺、化痰止咳</span></span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">枇杷花是保健中药，可以加蜂蜜冲泡保健茶饮：</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">枇杷花蜂蜜饮</span></span><span style="color: green;">；感冒咳嗽期间，可代茶饮缓解症状。（情况严重需就医，不可耽误）</span></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/9a7c9263fab17ca27e7ed96b1d6484f6.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">如果你经常吸烟，或长期待空调房，或夏天容易上火、咳嗽且痰多，那健康君建议干了这碗养生汤。</span></span></p><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">03、</span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">枇杷花瘦肉汤</span></span></span>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">干枇杷花50g、瘦肉400g、姜片3片</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">洗净枇杷花，再用1000毫升的水浸泡12h；把所有材料以及泡花水都装入炖盅，2小时后调味即可饮用。</span></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/8ed25f0b89d3e5f02e08a21a116cf67a.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">今天的枇杷妙用分享到这啦~</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">有上火，肺热咳嗽等症状的朋友，快把枇杷安排起来吧~</span></span></p>


</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
